    <div class="AssessmentProblem.identifier">102616</div>
    <div class="AssessmentProblem.type">RestrictedConstructedResponse</div>
    <div class="AssessmentProblem.statement"><p>The recipe for citrus punch says, &#x201C;Mix 3 cups of orange juice with 2 cups of lemonade.&#x201D; The recipe for tropical punch says, &#x201C;Mix 5 cups of pineapple juice with 1 cup of mango juice.&#x201D;</p>

<p>How much of each ingredient is needed to make the following numbers of batches of each kind of punch?&#xA0;Explain or show your reasoning.</p>

<ol>
	<li>a double batch</li>
	<li>half of a batch</li>
</ol>
</div>
    <div class="AssessmentProblem.solution"><ol>
	<li>6 cups orange juice, 4 cups lemonade and 10 cups pineapple juice, 2 cups mango juice</li>
	<li>
<span class="math math-repaired" data-png-file-id="3217">\(1\frac12\)</span> cups orange juice, 1 cup lemonade and <span class="math math-repaired" data-png-file-id="3280">\(2\frac12\)</span> cups pineapple juice, <span class="math math-repaired" data-png-file-id="238">\(\frac12\)</span> cup mango juice</li>
</ol>
</div>
